init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He thought about it for a few minutes and decided to call the number.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: It rang a few times and a man answered

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I need you to come with me to the future," he said.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: because the world was in danger.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So JFK told Barack he had to go to the future and learn how to use his powers.
